Text:
+ Newly renovated, clean and spacious apartments;
+ Girls at the reception very helpful;
- Extremely noisy: traffic noise from a very busy street (earplugs don't help), noise inside the building (neighbors talking, walking, etc. in the apartment below ours - were well heard);
- Smell of gas from the gas heater in our room (apartments are equipped with individual gas heaters to provide hot water);
- Cigarette smoke coming thru windows into the rooms from the inner yard where one of the administrators is constantly smoking.

