Text:
If you want some delicious desserts, great pizzas and some other stuff (risotto, salads etc.), this is the place to go ü•Ç
+ Service was great, very polite and kind stuff;
+ prices are totally normal (lunch for 3 people = 40 eurs);
+- food was great, especially dessert and pizza (they forgot one ingredient on one pizza but ok).
So, restaurant offers nice ambient, good prices, delicious food and kind stuff - why don't you try it? üòâ

